body:
This cast is technically incorrect until after the next line executes. Do

```ts
const forkedView: Omit<FuzzView, "currentSchema"> & Partial<Pick<FuzzView, "currentSchema">> = view.fork();
```

to accurately capture what's really going on, and then hopefully TS is smart enough to see that `forkedView` satisfies `FuzzView` after the next line executes.

If it doesn't, you can instead make a function like:

```ts
function asFuzzView(view: SchematizingTreeView, currentSchema): asserts view is FuzzView {
  type UnschematizedFuzzView = Omit<FuzzView, "currentSchema"> & Partial<Pick<FuzzView, "currentSchema">>;
  (view as UnschematizedFuzzView).currentSchema = currentSchema;
}
```

